Tatsuya: But Shinonome's right... We can't run! We have to fight!
Tatsuya: Alright, you guys! Let's do this!!!
EVER Members A & B: Yeah!
Tatsuya: W-We're going to give it everything we've got. Our determination's gotten us this far...
Taiga: Your determination...
Taiga: Well, you get points for spirit. Anyway, let's begin.
