Toya: (So much power...! In a split second, he swept everyone up in a torrent.)
Arata: I'm getting fed up with this.
Tatsuya: (You've gotta be kidding me... He just crushed us like a bug...)
Tatsuya: (We never stood a chance...)
Taiga: Alright, that should be enough. Next, you.
Kotaro: Eep...!
Kotaro: I-I'm not running either...! I'm gonna surpass RAD WEEKEND!
Kotaro: I'm not scared! I don't have time to be scared...!
Taiga: Haha. I like your bravery. Anyway, enough talk. Show me what you've got.
Kotaro: ...!
Kotaro: ♪~~~~!
An: ...!
Young Local Musicians: Yikes...! Who is that guy?! He's horrible!
