Taiga: Well, you left me no choice. After all, we shouldn't make these people here have to suffer through more of that.
An: ...
Arata: I suppose this means I'm next...
Young Local Musicians: Hey, it's Tono!
Young Local Musicians: Wait, didn't he battle against Taiga before? I remember him losing pretty badly, so I guess this is...
Taiga: Hey, Arata. Looks like you finally have a chance for a rematch with me.
Arata: Yes, it seems that way...
Arata: To be honest, I was hoping to win against you on an actual stage.
Arata: But I'm not letting this opportunity go. Not after learning the true reason RAD WEEKEND was so unnaturally intense.
Taiga: *Sigh* No fun, as usual. You've always got that cocky look on your face.
Arata: Not today. I still can't quite process the truth about Nagi.
Arata: Now that I know, I can't just go around half-heartedly saying that I'm going to surpass that night.
Arata: But I will surpass it. And now I say that knowing what it means.
Taiga: ...
